msgstr "there has been much rain in the desert up ahead. "

msgctxt "dn23:23.50"
msgid "Chaḍḍetha, bho, purāṇāni tiṇāni kaṭṭhāni udakāni, lahubhārehi sakaṭehi sīghaṃ sīghaṃ gacchatha; mā yoggāni kilamitthā”ti. "
msgstr "He advises us to toss out the grass, wood, and water. The wagons will move swiftly when lightly-laden, and won’t tire our draught teams. "

msgctxt "dn23:23.51"
msgid "Ayaṃ bho puriso neva amhākaṃ mitto, na ñātisālohito, kathaṃ mayaṃ imassa saddhāya gamissāma. "
msgstr "But this person is neither our friend nor relative. How can we proceed out of trust in him? "

msgctxt "dn23:23.52"
msgid "Na vo chaḍḍetabbāni purāṇāni tiṇāni kaṭṭhāni udakāni, yathābhatena bhaṇḍena satthaṃ payāpetha. "
msgstr "We shouldn’t toss out any grass, wood, or water, but continue with our goods laden as before. "

msgctxt "dn23:23.53"
msgid "Na no purāṇaṃ chaḍḍessāmā’ti. "
msgstr "We shall not toss out any old stock.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn23:23.54"
msgid "‘Evaṃ, bho’ti kho te satthikā tassa satthavāhassa paṭissutvā yathābhatena bhaṇḍena satthaṃ payāpesuṃ. "
msgstr "‘Yes, sir,’ the drivers replied, and they restarted the caravan with the goods laden as before. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn23:23.55"
msgid "Te paṭhamepi satthavāse na addasaṃsu tiṇaṃ vā kaṭṭhaṃ vā udakaṃ vā. "
